@page "/"
@inject SwiftClientApiEndpoint Endpoint

<PageTitle>Sekiban Swift Sample</PageTitle>

<h1>Sekiban DCB Swift Sample</h1>

<p class="lead">
    Blazor frontend for the Swift port of the Sekiban DCB Orleans Decider template. Every
    page below talks to the Swift Hummingbird ClientApi at
    <code>@Endpoint.BaseUrl</code>, which in turn forwards commits / queries to the generic
    <code>Sekiban.Dcb.WasmRuntime.Host</code> loading
    <code>sekiban-dcb-decider-swift.wasm</code>.
</p>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Domain pages</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="classrooms">Classrooms</a> — list / create via Swift
                <code>POST /api/classrooms</code> + MultiProjection readback.</li>
            <li><a href="students">Students</a> — list / create.</li>
            <li><a href="enrollments">Enrollments</a> — enroll / drop students across
                classrooms (Swift WASM multi-tag fan-out).</li>
            <li><a href="weather">Weather</a> — create / update location / delete.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Read-path diagnostics</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="mv">Materialized view status</a> — Postgres-direct MV registry +
                classrooms MV table.</li>
            <li><a href="memory">In-memory projection</a> — raw
                <code>GetClassRoomListQuery</code> output through MultiProjectionGrain.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-warning mt-4">
    <strong>Heads-up:</strong> Auth (<code>/auth/*</code>) is stubbed until Phase 3 of the
    Swift parity work lands. The Login page will render but calls to the Swift ClientApi's
    auth routes return 404; AuthApiClient swallows that silently so every other page works.
</div>
